title: 15 Minute Fat Burning HIIT Workout | Full Body at Home or Gym (No Equipment)
description:
A no equipment, super sweaty HIIT workout you can do anywhere and follow-along easily 🙏 For 45 more unique HIIT workouts all available in app form, and training + nutrition programmes approved by a world leading dietetics expert go to www.natachaoceane.com ❤️

The 15 minute HIIT workout: each exercise is performed for 30s and followed by 30s rest. It’s a circuit, so we complete Move 1, Move 2, Move 3, Move 4, Move 5 and then repeat for 3 total rounds.

1. Squat to knee drive
2. Reverse plank marches - see video for easier variation
3. Shoulder tap plank jacks - see video for easier variation
4. Kneel to squat thrust
5. Explosive jacks
